PASSWORD GENERATOR

Creating a command-line password generator in Python that generates random passwords based on user-defined criteria, such as length and character types (letters, numbers, symbols).More actions
Allow users to specify password length and character set preferences.

Features:

*Customizable password length

*Options to include/exclude uppercase letters, digits, and punctuation

*Utilizes the secrets module for cryptographically secure random number generation

*Ensures at least one character from each selected category is included.
